verbose_text: By contrast, we found that approximately 50 gene products were significantly downregulated upon the disruption of FgfrL1 expression, including wingless-type MMTV integration site family member 4 (Wnt4), dickkopf 1 (Dkk1), early growth response 1 (Egr1), Fgf8 and LIM homeobox 1 (Lhx1).
